My heart skips a beat seeing you leave.

1069
02:08:41,416 --> 02:08:44,457
Tomorrow your heart will be fine.

1070
02:08:45,250 --> 02:08:47,665
Believe me, young man.

1071
02:08:51,791 --> 02:08:55,499
I'll remember everything that happened
in this house as my souvenir.

1072
02:08:57,541 --> 02:08:59,165
Especially

1073
02:08:59,916 --> 02:09:03,207
the friendship you had for me.

1074
02:09:08,625 --> 02:09:13,999
And I'll remember to rub ice on my body
when the heat gets unbearable.

1075
02:09:15,666 --> 02:09:20,040
It's much more fun
to have a girl do that for you.

1076
02:09:22,208 --> 02:09:26,749
There won't be any girl
who can melt my ice...

1077
02:09:27,583 --> 02:09:31,832
like you could. I mean it.

1078
02:09:33,833 --> 02:09:38,915
Thank you. Thanks for everything.

1079
02:09:39,750 --> 02:09:41,665
Including...

1080
02:09:43,291 --> 02:09:46,332
When you lied to me about Kajorn.

1081
02:09:48,583 --> 02:09:50,665
How did you know?

1082
02:09:53,208 --> 02:09:57,582
I'm a witch. I have a crystal ball.

1083
02:09:59,375 --> 02:10:00,582
Let's go.

1084
02:10:01,458 --> 02:10:03,415
Bon voyage.

1085
02:10:22,208 --> 02:10:25,915
Ken, did you tell her about Mr. Kajorn?

1086
02:10:27,625 --> 02:10:29,249
I'd never dare do that!

1087
02:10:30,000 --> 02:10:31,207
How could she know then?

1088
02:10:32,208 --> 02:10:33,749
She knows a lot of people,

1089
02:10:34,375 --> 02:10:36,249
maybe one of
her Western friends told her.

1090
02:10:38,083 --> 02:10:40,749
Or maybe she really has a crystal ball.

1091
02:10:46,125 --> 02:10:50,665
Son of a bitch!
You'll never have your child!

1092
02:10:51,250 --> 02:10:55,957
May you burn in hell and be damned
until eternity!

1093
02:11:19,541 --> 02:11:20,874
She's gone.

1094
02:11:25,083 --> 02:11:29,165
My child... My child's gone too...

1095
02:11:32,416 --> 02:11:34,749
Yes.

1096
02:11:39,875 --> 02:11:45,165
My child's gone too!

1097
02:11:47,416 --> 02:11:52,249
My child.

1098
02:11:57,250 --> 02:11:58,957
My child.

1099
02:12:02,208 --> 02:12:04,499
And they all left me,

1100
02:12:04,791 --> 02:12:07,332
one by one...

1101
02:12:07,416 --> 02:12:09,874
like falling leaves.

1102
02:12:10,583 --> 02:12:16,040
Pree died when he was around 10.

1103
02:12:17,250 --> 02:12:18,957
You too, Ken.

1104
02:12:20,500 --> 02:12:22,415
I'm not dead yet.

1105
02:12:23,416 --> 02:12:27,040
I'm right here,
or do you take me for a ghost?

1106
02:12:28,666 --> 02:12:31,249
I'm not saying you're dead.

1107
02:12:32,791 --> 02:12:35,457
I said, everyone left me.

1108
02:12:37,375 --> 02:12:42,915
We all have to leave
those we love at some point, don't we?

1109
02:12:45,583 --> 02:12:46,790
I never did.

1110
02:12:47,708 --> 02:12:55,749
I never left Phijitvanich House.

1111
02:12:57,083 --> 02:13:02,790
You're talking about a house.
A house doesn't have a life.

1112
02:13:05,041 --> 02:13:06,249
Of course there is.

1113
02:13:06,375 --> 02:13:10,749
You don't see what I've seen.

1114
02:13:11,875 --> 02:13:15,582
Sometimes I saw Lord Wisnan.

1115
02:13:16,166 --> 02:13:19,124
I saw Aunt Wad, Madame Boonleung...

1116
02:13:19,750 --> 02:13:22,207
I saw Miss Kaew too, we even talked.

1117
02:13:22,583 --> 02:13:27,249
Don't you believe me?
I also saw Mr. Kajorn and Pree.

1118
02:13:29,000 --> 02:13:31,082
Are you serious?

1119
02:13:31,875 --> 02:13:34,624
You're frightening me!

1120
02:13:38,083 --> 02:13:39,332
I'm joking!

1121
02:13:46,541 --> 02:13:50,874
Ken, I have a present for you.

1122
02:13:51,416 --> 02:13:52,707
What is it?

1123
02:13:58,166 --> 02:13:58,999
Here.

1124
02:14:01,583 --> 02:14:04,540
My diary.

1125
02:14:05,458 --> 02:14:07,665
All my memories are written in here,

1126
02:14:08,125 --> 02:14:09,915
with pictures too.

1127
02:14:10,625 --> 02:14:14,415
And this is my will.

1128
02:14:14,791 --> 02:14:17,665
I give everything

1129
02:14:18,000 --> 02:14:21,415
to you and your children.

1130
02:14:23,416 --> 02:14:25,249
I'll take the diary,

1131
02:14:26,333 --> 02:14:30,040
but the will... I won't have it.

1132
02:14:30,625 --> 02:14:35,249
Are you out of your mind?
That's a few billion baht!

1133
02:14:36,833 --> 02:14:37,915
I won't take it.

1134
02:14:40,000 --> 02:14:45,415
I don't have a child,
I don't have anyone.

1135
02:14:45,875 --> 02:14:49,624
Give it to charity.

1136
02:14:50,583 --> 02:14:52,499
No, I want you to have it!

1137
02:14:52,583 --> 02:14:53,957
I don't want it!

1138
02:14:54,375 --> 02:14:55,749
I want you to have it!

1139
02:14:55,833 --> 02:14:59,124
I don't want it! You're so stubborn!

1140
02:14:59,750 --> 02:15:01,124
I should smack you!

1141
02:15:03,583 --> 02:15:05,249
Oh, I'm scared!

1142
02:15:05,875 --> 02:15:11,749
Are you mad
to refuse a billion-baht fortune?

1143
02:15:13,791 --> 02:15:15,332
Master Jan,

1144
02:15:15,916 --> 02:15:20,249
the apocalypse is coming.

1145
02:15:20,708 --> 02:15:22,624
What good

1146
02:15:23,458 --> 02:15:25,624
would money do?

1147
02:15:26,166 --> 02:15:27,582
Good afternoon, grandpa.

1148
02:15:28,791 --> 02:15:31,707
Tiwa, you're here.

1149
02:15:32,083 --> 02:15:32,915
Yes.

1150
02:15:34,375 --> 02:15:37,374
Is this Dao?

1151
02:15:37,958 --> 02:15:39,540
No.

1152
02:15:40,000 --> 02:15:43,165
This is Tiwa, Dao's son.

1153
02:15:43,708 --> 02:15:46,374
What kind of work do you do?

1154
02:15:47,500 --> 02:15:51,499
I work at NASA in the States.

1155
02:15:51,916 --> 02:15:55,290
Tiwa has a PhD. In physics.

1156
02:15:57,583 --> 02:16:01,999
Grandpa,
we have to leave for the airport now.

1157
02:16:04,250 --> 02:16:05,957
Where are you off to?

1158
02:16:07,041 --> 02:16:09,582
Back home in the USA.

1159
02:16:15,250 --> 02:16:18,624
I have to go, or I'll miss my flight.

1160
02:16:23,416 --> 02:16:24,915
Let me hold it.

1161
02:16:25,708 --> 02:16:28,124
See, everybody left me.

1162
02:16:28,458 --> 02:16:30,290
Don't say that, Master Jan.

1163
02:16:31,166 --> 02:16:34,374
I come back to visit you every year.

1164
02:16:34,916 --> 02:16:39,249
If I dropped dead this year,
you wouldn't see me here next year.

1165
02:16:40,083 --> 02:16:42,249
Then I'd see you in heaven.

1166
02:16:43,791 --> 02:16:45,207
You mean hell?

1167
02:16:45,750 --> 02:16:50,249
Heaven or hell,
I'll make sure to see you every year.

1168
02:16:50,791 --> 02:16:52,915
What if you died first?

1169
02:16:54,708 --> 02:16:57,582
I'd come to you as a ghost.

1170
02:16:58,750 --> 02:17:02,415
Please don't, I'd be so scared.

1171
02:17:03,333 --> 02:17:05,249
We really have to go.

1172
02:17:06,833 --> 02:17:09,165
Please take care of him.

1173
02:17:09,708 --> 02:17:10,832
Don't worry, sir.

1174
02:17:11,291 --> 02:17:14,915
See you soon,

1175
02:17:15,500 --> 02:17:16,915
in heaven or hell.

1176
02:17:17,000 --> 02:17:19,915
Hell, definitely.

1177
02:17:20,833 --> 02:17:23,249
Who knows?

1178
02:17:23,750 --> 02:17:25,915
Hell, wanna bet?

1179
02:17:26,375 --> 02:17:29,582
- Goodbye.
- Be careful.

1180
02:17:49,958 --> 02:17:52,082
Bon voyage, Ken.
